		<description><![CDATA[In a new Spanish-language ad to begin airing on Thursday, a liberal advocacy group invokes Mr. Trump's negative comments about Hispanics to criticize Mr. McCain, who is facing re-election to the Senate, for refusing to act on President Obama's nomination of Judge Merrick B. Garland to the Supreme Court.]]></description>
